title: [Azuma Tesshin] Hoshigarina Imouto CH05 [English translated by T
description:
This is a fun little story commissioned by Bre. It's a short story by Azuma Tesshin, taken from his tankoubon "Hoshigarina Imouto."

Some one-shot stories have characters that I wish the author developed further into other stories/chapters. This is one such story.

Many thanks to Bre for commissioning me for this! It was a fun one to work on!

And many thanks to those who help seed! ^_^
